Evolution of deployment:
------------------------
    Traditional -> Virtualization -> Containers

    -) Traditional Deployment: Setup
       Hardware -> OS -> Application

       Example:
       ---------
       one server (big machine)
       install OS (linux/windows)
       deploy your app (war file)

       Problem here:
       -------------
       you use very little resources
        server = 128GB RAM
        app uses only 4BG
       can't run multiple apps safely

       No isolation: (Example)
       ------------------------
       2 apps using same java (JVM)
       one crashes --> other alos affected
